xtended\nsources due to the presence of a nearby or partially resolved companion. The\nSLoWPoKES-II catalog is publicly available to the entire community on the world\nwide web via the Filtergraph data visualization portal.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 20 Apr 2015 22:17:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 22 Apr 2015 13:31:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-08-06"}
