res of equilibrium shapes in\nthe ADE and spontaneous curvature models, like budding behaviour or starfish\nforms, behave in a shear flow.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 21 Apr 2015 13:24:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 13 Oct 2015 08:42:20 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 27 Oct 2015 18:12:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-11-11"}
